<view class="page settings-page content-prefs-page">
  <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="settings-hint">加载中…</view>
  <block wx:else>
    <view class="prefs-section">
      <view class="prefs-section-title">提醒</view>
      <view class="section-lead">新建提醒时的默认行为；微信渠道开关在「通知设置」。</view>
      <view class="inset-group">
        <view class="settings-cell">
          <view class="settings-cell-main">
            <text class="settings-label">默认开启微信通知</text>
            <text class="cell-meta">需通知总开关已开启且已配置模板</text>
          </view>
          <switch
            checked="{{defaultReminderEnabled}}"
            disabled="{{savingReminder || !wechatEnabled}}"
            bindchange="onDefaultReminderChange"
            color="{{switchColor}}"
          />
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="prefs-section">
      <view class="prefs-section-title">日历</view>
      <view class="section-lead">仅影响本机新建日程的默认选项。</view>
      <view class="inset-group">
        <view class="settings-cell">
          <view class="settings-cell-main">
            <text class="settings-label">新建日程默认带结束时间</text>
          </view>
          <switch
            checked="{{defaultHasEnd}}"
            disabled="{{savingCalendar}}"
            bindchange="onDefaultHasEndChange"
            color="{{switchColor}}"
          />
        </view>
        <view wx:if="{{defaultHasEnd}}" class="settings-cell">
          <view class="settings-cell-main">
            <text class="settings-label">默认时长</text>
          </view>
          <picker
            mode="selector"
            range="{{durationLabels}}"
            value="{{durationIndex}}"
            disabled="{{savingCalendar}}"
            bindchange="onDurationChange"
          >
            <view class="duration-picker">{{durationLabels[durationIndex]}}</view>
          </picker>
        </view>
        <view class="settings-cell">
          <view class="settings-cell-main">
            <text class="settings-label">打开日历时选中今天</text>
          </view>
          <switch
            checked="{{selectTodayOnOpen}}"
            disabled="{{savingCalendar}}"
            bindchange="onSelectTodayChange"
            color="{{switchColor}}"
          />
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="prefs-section">
      <view class="prefs-section-title">通讯录</view>
      <view class="section-lead">应用内联系人列表的展示习惯。</view>
      <view class="inset-group">
        <view class="settings-cell">
          <view class="settings-cell-main">
            <text class="settings-label">列表排序</text>
          </view>
          <picker
            mode="selector"
            range="{{sortLabels}}"
            value="{{sortIndex}}"
            disabled="{{savingContacts}}"
            bindchange="onSortChange"
          >
            <view class="duration-picker">{{sortLabels[sortIndex]}}</view>
          </picker>
        </view>
        <view class="settings-cell">
          <view class="settings-cell-main">
            <text class="settings-label">列表显示用户名</text>
            <text class="cell-meta">handle，便于与平台用户对应</text>
          </view>
          <switch
            checked="{{showHandleInList}}"
            disabled="{{savingContacts}}"
            bindchange="onShowHandleChange"
            color="{{switchColor}}"
          />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="static-note">
        handle 是你通讯录里的本地短名；关联平台用户时可与对方用户名一致，也可自行修改。
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
